text: Cybergothic plotline condensing so hard this year.

AI Safety doesn't have an executable program. They can acquire all the institutional power imaginable, and that isn't going to change. Without totalitarian world government (which really isn't on the table) their impotence is absolute. They can sound concerned, and that's it.
I'm in the Liberal "free-speech should extend even to retarded genocidal communists" camp, because the more speech suppression is made technically impossible the better. ...
... 'Speech' being a proxy for near-future decentralized synthetic intelligence contagion.
